divs: Sighting DetailsI was going into old pictures and came across 2 pics in the everglades. At the time I did not notice the orb. I was looking at the picture to delete it and I see the orb. I thought it was just some flare but I saw another one. I'm sorry I cant remember everything from that day but I do remember parts of that day. I still have the pics.. No they are not altered at all......
